window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Disney’s <i>Encanto</i> is the tale of an extraordinary family that lives hidden in the mountains of Colombia in a wondrous, charmed place called an Encanto. Everyone in the Madrigal family has a unique gift, ranging from superstrength to the power to heal. Everyone except Mirabel.&nbsp;</p> <p>But when the magic surrounding the Encanto is in danger, Mirabel decides she might just be her exceptional family’s last hope. <i>Encanto: The Junior Novelization</i> retells the vibrant story!</p>"; 
